    h2 General usage
    p You can add the "html" parameter in the URL query string to have an HTML view of the results. Example:
    a(href='/api/public/users/sciper/150938?html') /api/public/users/sciper/150938?html

    h3 Tips
    p: #[span Install] #[a(href="http://jsonview.com/") JSONview] #[plugin for your browser. It will simplify a lot the viewing of API pages!]

